E.S.P. Hadouken
===============

Drawings stole your Game Boy!

Guide the dot through each drawing's randomized barrage without touching the
deadly void.


Requirements
------------

* Python
* pygame
* NumPy


Running
-------

Run this command from the root of the package:

    ./esp-hado


Installation
------------

On Linux, run this command as root:

    python setup.py install


Instructions
------------

Guide the dot with the arrow keys or using your joypad

### Keyboard Controls ###

ARROWS or WASD  move
ENTER           confirm, pause
F1              reset
F2              mute


